            </a>
            <div class="project-card__body">
              <h3 class="project-card__title"><a href="https://pilasports.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="project-name-link">Player Invite &amp; League Arranger - PILA Sports</a></h3>
              <p class="text-section">Developed the full brand identity and UI/UX for PILA — a pickleball league management platform. Handled everything from visual direction and logo design to interface layout and the overall site experience.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="project-card">
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/rescue8tradingphils" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="project-card__image">
              <img src={`${base}rescue-8.jpg`} alt="Rescue 8 Trading Philippines, Inc." loading="lazy" width="800" height="500" />
            </a>
            <div class="project-card__body">
              <h3 class="project-card__title"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/rescue8tradingphils" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="project-name-link">Rescue 8 Trading Philippines, Inc.</a></h3>
              <p class="text-section">A WooCommerce-powered WordPress site with a custom template — designed and built to present products and services with an integrated online store, clean layout, and straightforward navigation.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="project-card">
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/rideslowlifestyle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="project-card__image">
              <img src={`${base}ride-slow.jpg`} alt="Ride Slow Lifestyle" loading="lazy" width="800" height="500" />
            </a>
            <div class="project-card__body">
              <h3 class="project-card__title"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/rideslowlifestyle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="project-name-link">Ride Slow Lifestyle</a></h3>
              <p class="text-section">An image-forward WordPress layout featuring WooCommerce integration, a photo gallery, and real-time Facebook Messenger — built to support promotion, sales, and active community engagement.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <!-- Row 2: Digital & Branding -->
          <div class="project-group-label" data-aos="fade-up">Digital & Branding Projects</div>

          <article class="project-card">
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/kademyahanfoodhouse/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="project-card__image">
              <img src={`${base}kademyahan.png`} alt="Kademyahan Food House" loading="lazy" width="800" height="500" />
            </a>
            <div class="project-card__body">
              <h3 class="project-card__title"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/kademyahanfoodhouse/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="project-name-link">Kademyahan Food House</a></h3>
              <p class="text-section">Brand identity for a local food house in Sta. Maria, Bulacan — designed the logo and visual direction used across public-facing materials including menus, labels, and promotional collateral.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="project-card">
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/adyophilippines" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="project-card__image">
              <img src={`${base}adyo.jpg`} alt="Adyó Philippines" loading="lazy" width="800" height="500" />
            </a>
            <div class="project-card__body">
              <h3 class="project-card__title"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/adyophilippines" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="project-name-link">Adyó Philippines</a></h3>
