            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="project-card">
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/project1998co" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="project-card__image">
              <img src={`${base}project-1998.png`} alt="Project 1998 Apparel Co." loading="lazy" width="800" height="400" />
            </a>
            <div class="project-card__body">
              <h3 class="project-card__title"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/project1998co" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="project-name-link">Project 1998 Apparel Co.</a></h3>
              <p class="text-section">Brand identity for a local PH clothing and bag brand — covering logo, visual language, and design direction rooted in street-ready style and everyday wearability.</p>
