              and the craft of the perfect custom build. It's one part engineering, one part creative expression.
            </p>
            <p class="content-paragraph" data-aos="reveal-left" data-aos-duration="700" data-aos-delay="100">
              Every board is a statement piece. From <strong>thocky linears</strong> to <strong>crisp tactiles</strong>,
              each build merges <strong>engineering precision with creative expression</strong> — the intersection
