              Cryptobuds is a crypto community group I co-founded — built around education, honest discussion, and navigating the web3 space together. What started as a small circle of enthusiasts grew into a network of members sharing insights on DeFi, NFTs, and emerging blockchain projects. The goal was never hype — it was building literacy and trust in a noisy space.
