        <div>
          <p class="statement-outline">THE DEVELOPER<br />BEHIND THE WORK.</p>
        </div>
        <p class="statement-solid" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300" data-aos-duration="800">
          Thoughtful systems. Interfaces that <strong>respect the user</strong>. Code that feels <strong>intentional</strong>. Always building, always learning.
